{
  "chapter": 28,
  "chapter_summary": "本章围绕芮玮在白堡的冲突展开。胡异凡因儿子胡天星被芮玮打伤肩骨，带领十八名弟子围攻芮玮，芮玮以天遁剑法轻松击败众弟子。混战中，林琼菊为救公公胡异凡而挥剑，却误刺丈夫胡天星致其重伤，胡异凡悲痛欲绝。胡异凡迁怒于二人，放火要将芮玮和林琼菊活活烧死，二人冲破屋顶逃出白堡。芮玮带受伤的林琼菊逃至连阳城客栈养伤，期间悉心照料。林琼菊透露她的剑法\"伤心剑\"系驼叟所传，但因毒誓不可传授他人。芮玮得知天下仅林琼菊会此剑法，欲学却遭拒。章末一位神秘道士出现在客栈，寻找残疾老头。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……们要做什么？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你公公被这小子打碎肩骨，非叫他偿命不可！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不……不行……你们不能将他杀死……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tian_xing",
      "speaker_name": "胡天星",
      "listener": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "text": "怎么不行，我不是请你下来相助爹爹的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": "char_hu_tian_xing",
      "text": "当然不行啦！我们要杀你的情人，你自是不愿意。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tian_xing",
      "speaker_name": "胡天星",
      "listener": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "text": "谁……谁是她的情人？……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": "char_hu_tian_xing",
      "text": "笨蛋！早就戴了绿帽子还不知道，快将那臭小子杀了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tian_xing",
      "speaker_name": "胡天星",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好家伙！原来是你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": "char_hu_tian_xing",
      "text": "徒儿们，一起上罢！对付这种人不用客气。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父往日不是常说自己和敌人相斗时，严禁旁人相助吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别打！别打……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "text": "着！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "text": "躺下！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你……你……竟敢帮助奸夫谋杀亲夫……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你……你……也会海渊剑法？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_hu_tian_xing",
      "text": "我……我……没心伤你……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "臭女人，别在老子面前假惺惺，还我儿子命来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "text": "你儿子不是她杀，别冤枉她……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "奸人，你也一起陪命吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "text": "公公别打了，天星快死了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": "char_hu_tian_xing",
      "text": "星儿，你不能死……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你快去看看，他的伤势如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "谁要你来的？谁要你来的……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你抱我走吧，我不要死在这里。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "没有关系，箭射得不深，你不会死的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不会死，我也不要再呆在这里，他们要杀我，还留在这里有什么意思？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你跑出去，他们不知当做是我，误伤了你，不会存心要射你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "一定存心！一定存心！你没有看到刚才公公一刀要将我杀了吗？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "他一时气愤出手，你别当真。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我杀了他儿子，他是不会放过我，凭着咱们幼时相交一场，送我回到爹爹那里。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "这件事我要向你公公说明，不能怪你，他知道你那一剑收势不住后，自会原谅。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不送我走，是一定要看我被杀啦……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "不会的！不会的！你别瞎疑心……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我出去给你找点食物。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "外面的弓箭手还没退吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不让咱们出去，是什么意思？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公公以为我婚前不贞，是定要将我活活饿死。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "text": "他胡猜疑，明天弓箭手再不撤退，我抱你冲出去，找他理论！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们放火！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "要烧死咱们！要烧死咱们！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一对奸夫淫妇活活烧死，陪葬我的儿子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！他儿子果然死了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这时管他儿子死不死，咱们快想法逃出去呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小玮，你要等死吗？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "快射！快射！奸夫淫妇逃出来了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡异凡",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "别逃，还我儿子命来……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "白堡众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "捉奸夫淫妇呀！捉拿奸夫淫妇呀……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你送我回黑堡好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我再也不去黑堡。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "为什么呀？你从小住在黑堡，送我回去一趟不好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "等我再回黑堡时，不会放过你爹爹！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你……你……还要杀我爹爹……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我爹爹再对你不起，总有十年养育之恩，你！你不该再对他老人家记仇……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "十年是我忍辱偷生，要想找机会行刺，说不上养育的恩德！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "但那年我救你一次，你就不记得吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我记得那年救我的事，你救我，我也救你，但与上一代仇恨不相干，除非我死了，不然非杀林三寒不可！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那你现在已经救我一命，算是回报当年救你一命啦？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "可以这么说！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你还是不要救我的好，让我早早死在白堡好了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不送我回黑堡，总可以送我回山西吧？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "要是我身体完全无妨，我就自个回山西，也用不着你送！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "就因你身体没有完全恢复，我才不能送你回山西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "是什么原因？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "三个月后，我在闽东有个约会非到不可，山西此地来回快马三个月赶得及，但你身体却不能快马赶路啊？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那等约会后，再回山西好了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥练的是什么剑法？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "这招剑法叫不破剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我看来好熟，是不是那天你以这招剑法将我一剑挡去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你那一剑可是海渊剑法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么海渊剑法？我不知道，但我那一剑叫做伤心剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伤心剑？伤心剑……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "是一个什么样的人教你这招伤心剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "是个身材高大的老头教的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "他身上可有什么特征？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有啦！他身材虽高，却长得驼背弓腰，看来也不太高了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！他是驼叟，他怎会传你那招伤心剑？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "人家可不像你，知恩不图报，有一次在堡外见他饿倒路旁快要死了，扶他到堡中饱餐一顿，他要离去时，说我心肠好无他物可报，就将一招最得意的剑法传我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "他传你剑法，可有请你赴约？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "没有啊！但在临走前他似乎开口说过一句二年之约，但末说完，便蹒跚离去，看他走路都走不稳，看来活不多久！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此看来，他自己不能赴约，会以谁来代赴约呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "赴什么约呀？你说给我听听？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你不知道，就不要问！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好！你这样，我决不理你了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "菊妹，你那招伤心剑可不可以教我？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "别和我说话，我不理你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "可是你愿意教我了？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不是小妹不愿教你，实因那年驼背老人传我剑法时，叫我发了一个毒誓，说要是传别人，必……必定终生不育……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "算了，你记着不要再传给别人，是因为这招剑法十分厉害，若让歹人学到，为害不浅。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伙计，最近有没有看到七八十左右的残疾老头来到这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    }
